  "body": "Elasticity is an important feature for cloud native stateless apps such as the one deployed out of the box with helm create.  Allowing users to easily autoscale newly created apps would be beneficial.\r\n\r\nI propose we add a disabled by default hpa, with default values of 1 to 100 replicas and 80% cpu utilization threshold.\r\n\r\ncc @helm/chart-maintainers\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
